description:
Danny recaps this week's Real Housewives of Potomac with VERY special guest Gabourey Sidibe (Precious)! Gabourey stars in the upcoming Antebellum and is here to talk all things Potomac. They discuss Wendy's feud with Ashley, Karen and Ray, Gizelle stirring the pot, and so much more! Plus, they talk about Gabourey working with Queen Mariah, mental health, and writing!


Watch this episode on YOUTUBE: YouTube.com/DannyPellegrino1
